    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>A compact, semi-crystalline magnesian limestone from Minnesota, ranging in color from buff, cream, yellow, gray, pink, or reddish buff. It is commonly used for building as well as for decoration.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
